data.description: Come check out this spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home located in a wonderful Wylie ISD neighborhood, just a few doors down from the neighborhood pool! The interior features a split bedroom floorplan, with an open concept kitchen, dining, and living. Stainless appliances and an island in the kitchen. High ceilings throughout! The master bathroom has a walk-in shower, soaker tub, and a long corner vanity with double sinks. The exterior features a new roof put on in the summer of 2023, a sprinkler system, and rain gutters. All of this and much more!
